<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Austere" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Austere,</orth> severe, rigid, stern: <cit><quote>this a. insociable life,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.809" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 809</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with most a. sanctimony,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.59" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 59</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>an a. regard of control,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 2.5.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 5, 73</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>of grave and a. quality,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 54</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>